Acme-Abuse version 0.02
=======================

This module allows to create a setid perl interpreter which will
handle all calls to a given package.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

     Storable, Filter::Simple

